headline: BlackRock Expands Outcome Product Suite to Meet Increasing Investor Demand
summary: NEW YORK, October 01, 2025--Today, BlackRock bolstered its Outcome ETF suite with the launch of the iShares Large Cap 10% Target Buffer ETFs. The first ETF in the series, the iShares Large Cap 10% Target Buffer Sep ETF (CBOE:STEN), begins trading today, while the remaining funds will be listed later this month.
